<P><FONT SIZE=4><I><B>Collect (ECUSA): </B></I></FONT>
</P>
<P><FONT SIZE=5>A</FONT>lmighty God, whose Son our Savior Jesus
Christ is the light of the world: Grant that your people, illumined
by your Word and Sacraments, may shine with the radiance of Christ&sup1;s
glory, that he may be known, worshipped, and obeyed to the ends of
the earth; through Jesus Christ our Lord, who with you and the Holy
Spirit lives and reigns, one God, now and for ever. Amen. 
</P>
<P><FONT SIZE=5>A</FONT>lmighty God, <BR>Your Son our Savior Jesus
Christ is the light of the world.<BR>Make us shine with the radiance
of Christ's glory<BR>so that those who know us may come to know
him<BR>through Jesus Christ our Lord, who with you and the Holy
Spirit lives and reigns, one God, now and for ever. Amen. 
</P>
